title: Void
body:
read it on the AO3 at https://ift.tt/2OqFvP2

by B00kw0rm10

Alain Labelle only really loved one person; Clint Barton.

So, when Clint is taken from him by a psychotic God devoted to controlling Earth, he’s naturally upset. Then again, the last thing he expected was to garner the attention of the Avengers and all of their enemies.

Alain Labelle is attuned to the power of the stones.

Alain Labelle is nothingness. Alain Labelle is void.

And Void is coveted by death.
